FLAG_FULLSCREEN - Static variable in class io.ichi_go.ichigo.util.SystemUiHider
When this flag is set, SystemUiHider.show() and SystemUiHider.hide() will toggle the visibility of the status bar.
FLAG_HIDE_NAVIGATION - Static variable in class io.ichi_go.ichigo.util.SystemUiHider
When this flag is set, SystemUiHider.show() and SystemUiHider.hide() will toggle the visibility of the navigation bar, if it's present on the device and the device allows hiding it.
FLAG_LAYOUT_IN_SCREEN_OLDER_DEVICES - Static variable in class io.ichi_go.ichigo.util.SystemUiHider
When this flag is set, the WindowManager.LayoutParams.FLAG_LAYOUT_IN_SCREEN flag will be set on older devices, making the status bar "float" on top of the activity layout.
